Package: coriM
Type: Package
Title: Provides Monthly Interpolations Using IDW
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Guisseppe A. Vasquez Villano
Maintainer: Guisseppe A. Vasquez Villano <guisseppe.19@hotmail.com>
Description: The coriM package is designed to perform monthly interpolations using the Inverse Distance Weighting (IDW) method. It utilizes temperature records obtained from various weather stations.
